title: The quality of streaming media played online is poor. Why?
answer:
l   The source files of the streaming media are of poor quality. 


 l   The network connection is weak. 

 l   Your phone hardware is faulty. For example, the display is damaged. To verify the problem, play a local video. 

 l   The memory of your phone is insufficient. 

 l   The CPU usage is high. 

 l   Your phone is running too many applications.
